      • genreDataUpload

        public static java.lang.String genreDataUpload​(java.lang.String uploadFile)
                                        throws java.io.FileNotFoundException,
                                               java.sql.SQLException
        The method manages upload into the genre table in the database. The database is logged into before data is read line by line from uploadFile, split into separate attributes and inserted into the genre table using a defined query.
        Parameters:
        uploadFile - Location of file from which to upload
        Returns:
        String returned to calling code outlining data uploaded
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - if data file cannot be accessed.
        java.sql.SQLException - if DriverManager.getConnection unable to successfully execute update.
